description: This month, we are excited to host Carol Willing who will be discussing the Jupyter eco-sytem.  Carol develops software, electronics, educational tutorials, and is passionate about outreach.  She is a core developer on the Jupyter Project and is a former director at the Python Software foundation.  She continues to contribute her time to OpenHatch, Systers, PyLadies San Diego, and San Diego Python.
title: Taming Big Data with Jupyter and Friends
